{
  "stem": "802.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If we don't survive, it doesn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in fact, even prior to that, during the period when we're attending the so-called schools, you know, when we went to each other's house, my mother sort of almost pleaded with my-- with my father to leave us alone, because we're hungry.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and-- and my father insisted that we study.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he said that this will keep our mind off the unfolding tragedies, of the horrors, the daily horrors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And indeed, he was right in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And also, if we survive, there was always the hope of surviving.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One doesn't-- one never believes that one is going to die.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I shouldn't say that for everyone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I certainly did not believe that I was going to die in the concentration camps, whereas my sister did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She didn't think she would survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And yet, she was the stronger of the two of us, physically and emotionally.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As I told you, she's really an extraordinary woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had French.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And indeed, it did-- I'll never forget--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] --when I-- when I was in undergraduate school I needed several languages because I wanted to go to graduate school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and my-- my discipline is-- is comparative literature, so you need languages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I already had some priming, you know. and of course, the Latin that I learned, that I studied before also was very, very useful to me later.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was useful in more than a practical way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was useful-- again, I don't want to use the term spiritual, but I don't know what other term to-- to use.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was a kind of con-- con-- continuation of my father's values.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
